## Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Success |
|--------|----------|-------------|---------|
| GET | `/health` | Health check | 200 |
| GET | `/api/notes` | List all notes | 200 |
| GET | `/api/notes/:id` | Get note by id | 200 |
| POST | `/api/notes` | Create new note | 201 |
| PATCH | `/api/notes/:id` | Update note | 200 |
| DELETE | `/api/notes/:id` | Delete note | 204 |